      • parameters

        public Prepared parameters()
        Description copied from interface: PushConnector
        Every push connector has a set of output parameters used to configure the destination. It is expected that this method will return a map of the form

        output_params.variable-name ==> value

        Each connector implementation should* do it's own verification of the map's contents
